 Notification notification = new Notification();         notification.when = System.currentTimeMillis();         notification.flags |= Notification.FLAG_AUTO_CANCEL;         notification.flags |= Notification.FLAG_SHOW_LIGHTS;          notification.ledOffMS = 1500;         notification.ledOnMS = 1500;         return notification;      } } </code></pre>  <p>Please explain me the working of these concepts.. any help would mean me alot</p>  <p>thanks a lot</p>